OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779379877
OL,3,CEx-England boss McClaren joins
OL,4,CRotherham as 'head of football'
OL,6,FFormer England manager Steve McClaren
OL,7,Fhas been given a newly created job as
OL,8,Fhead of football at League Two
OL,9,FRotherham United.
OL,11,FThe club said the 65-year-old would be
OL,12,Fresponsible for "strategic leadership"
OL,13,F- including the recruitment of a new
OL,14,Fmanager - following their relegation
OL,15,Ffrom League One.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
