OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779379877
OL,3,CEx-England boss McClaren joins
OL,4,CRotherham as 'head of football'
OL,6,FChairman Tony Stewart said: "Steve
OL,7,Fwill provide the board with a new
OL,8,Fvoice and a pair of eyes and ears that
OL,9,Fhave seen how clubs ensure that they
OL,10,Freach optimal performance at both the
OL,11,Ftop club level and on the
OL,12,Finternational stage.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
