FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779379877
OL,3,CEx-England boss McClaren joins
OL,4,CRotherham as 'head of football'
OL,6,F"We acknowledged that as part of our
OL,7,Fongoing efforts to drive standards and
OL,8,Fkeep the football club progressing
OL,9,Fforwards off-the-pitch that adding
OL,10,Fsomeone with such impressive football
OL,11,Fknowledge would be highly beneficial
OL,12,Fat board level and to attract someone
OL,13,Fof Steve's calibre hopefully shows to
OL,14,Four fans that we are determined to
OL,15,Fmake positive changes following
OL,16,Fdifficult years recently."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
