PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779379877
OL,3,CEx-England boss McClaren joins
OL,4,CRotherham as 'head of football'
OL,6,FMcClaren, twice a former assistant
OL,7,Fmanager at Manchester United, was
OL,8,FEngland boss between 2006 and 2007 and
OL,9,Fwas most recently in charge of
OL,10,FJamaica's national team.
OL,12,FHe joins Rotherham after manager Lee
OL,13,FClark left the club earlier this
OL,14,Fmonth, having expected to stay on in
OL,15,Fhis position.
OL,17,FThe Millers were relegated to League
OL,18,FTwo after finishing second from bottom
OL,19,Fof League One.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
