FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779379877
OL,3,CEx-England boss McClaren joins
OL,4,CRotherham as 'head of football'
OL,6,FMcClaren has a long-standing
OL,7,Ffriendship with Mr Stewart and has
OL,8,Fdiscussed the possibility of joining
OL,9,Fas manager on several occasions in the
OL,10,Fpast.
OL,12,FMr Stewart added: "Looking at the
OL,13,Fbigger picture of the football club,
OL,14,FSteve's official appointment to the
OL,15,Frole of head of football will, without
OL,16,Fdoubt, serve as the first step in what
OL,17,Fwill now be a series of decisions
OL,18,Facross the footballing operation in an
OL,19,Fimportant summer for the club."
OL,26,@tD@SOU
